<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جُنُودٌ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُمُ:</span> الأَحْزَابُ حِينَ اجْتَمَعُوا فِي غَزْوَةِ الخَنْدَقِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زَاغَتِ الْأَبْصَارُ}</span> ... شَخَصَتِ الأَبْصَارُ؛ حَيْرَةً وَدَهْشَةً.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الظُّنُونَا}</span> ... تَظُنُّونَ أَنَّ اللهَ لَا يَنْصُرُ دِينَهُ وَنَبِيَّهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
