<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَزُلْزِلُوا}</span> ... اضْطَرَبُوا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّرَضٌ}</span> ... شَكٌّ، وَضَعْفُ إِيمَانٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غُرُورًا}</span> ... بَاطِلًا خَادِعًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَثْرِبَ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> الاِسْمُ الجَاهِلِيُّ لِلْمَدِينَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا مُقَامَ لَكُمْ}</span> ... لَا إِقَامَةَ لَكُمْ فِي مَعْرَكَةٍ خَاسِرَةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَوْرَةٌ}</span> ... غَيْرُ مُحَصَّنَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَقْطَارِهَا}</span> ... جَوَانِبِ المَدِينَةِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
